  "id": "RAW_66fdd26b",
  "title": "从「偶然发现」走向「必然创造」：AI 如何重塑生物制造全链路？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5ODEzMjIyMA==&mid=2247730716&idx=2&sn=f5386fa1a8dc917a1997e940b36d6f7f",
  "date": "2026-01-17 09:52:00",
